message.content: cs.IR, cs.DB, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG. The paper deals with entity retrieval, which is a subfield of information retrieval (IR) and database (DB) systems. It also involves natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning (ML) techniques, which are relevant to the sub-categories of computational linguistics (CL), artificial intelligence (AI), and machine learning (LG).
